@olegz just pushed up a commit with some changes from the last round of feedback (renaming jarFile, fixing empty catch block, fixing empty IllegalArgumentException).

Have you had a chance to test this out? 

Also let me know if/when you want me to squash the commits

@brosander was able to run tests to generate certs with prefix and suffix

+1

Will merge into master shortly

@mcgilman  I think it makes sense to use the ellipsis for view state too.

@scottyaslan I'm still seeing the scrollable class applied on the Add Processor description as well, so I can both scroll _and_ hover to see the full description.

Also, can we apply the the styling that I outlined in my earlier jira comment to all these areas? This way both behavior and design will be consistent.

